      <pattern value="(((20(([02468][048])|([13579][26]))-02-29))|(20[0-9][0-9])-((((0[1-9])|(1[0-2]))-((0[1-9])|(1\d)|(2[0-8])))|((((0[13578])|(1[02]))-31)|(((0[1,3-9])|(1[0-2]))-(29|30)))))"></pattern>
